fr.sii.ogham.testing.sms.simulator.bean

Enum Alphabet

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Alphabet>
      • fr.sii.ogham.testing.sms.simulator.bean.Alphabet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Alphabet>

    public enum Alphabet
extends Enum<Alphabet>
    This is enum of the alphabet type. Alphabet represents the lower 4 bits of the data_coding field in the PDU, as specified in s5.2.19 of the SMPP v3.4 specification.
    Author:
    Aur√©lien Baudet
